messageBody:
Brought to you by StickyMinds.com and Better Software magazine
* Sponsored by Telelogic * As organizations struggle with financial
management and fewer resources in a complex, global economy, effective
software delivery remains a key driver for success, including:
* Efficient management of global teams
* Close communication and collaboration across disparate groups
* Improved agile interaction and quality for fewer product defects and
reduced costs

Attend Telelogic's ALM Webcast for actionable insights on how to improve
your software development strategies. Join us May 28, at 11 a.m. ET.
Register and attend this Web seminar to be automatically entered into
our drawing for a iPod Shuffle!
